    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "question": "In resolving x² / ((x-1)²(x+2)), the highest power factor is (x-1)². For A/(x-1) + B/(x-1)² + C/(x+2), B is calculated directly by cover-up with x=1. What about A?",
      "difficulty": "Hard",
      "hasDiagram": false,
      "diagram_description": "",
      "options": {
        "A": "It requires taking a derivative or comparing coefficients",
        "B": "Cover-up method works for A too",
