        "D": "A = B"
      },
      "answer": "A",
      "pyq": false
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "question": "For an expression f(x)/Q(x), if Q(x) is expanded as xⁿ + ..., the number of unknown partial fraction constants exactly equals the ______ of Q(x).",
