    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "question": "If the roots of the denominator are α₁, α₂, ..., α_n, and P(α_i) ≠ 0, and Q(x) = (x-α₁)(x-α₂)...(x-α_n), then the term A_i/(x-α_i) has A_i = ______.",
